create_time.description: The time when the subnet was created. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits. Examples: '2014-10-02T15:01:23Z' and '2014-10-02T15:01:23.045123456Z'.

description.description: A free-text description of the resource. Max length 1024 characters.

effective_labels.description: All of labels (key/value pairs) present on the resource in GCP, including the labels configured through Terraform, other clients and services.

labels.description: Labels associated with this resource. **Note**: This field is non-authoritative, and will only manage the labels present in your configuration. Please refer to the field 'effective_labels' for all of the labels present on the resource.

location.description: The Google Cloud region to which the target Distributed Cloud Edge zone belongs.

mtu.description: IP (L3) MTU value of the network. Default value is '1500'. Possible values are: '1500', '9000'.

name.description: The canonical name of this resource, with format 'projects/{{project}}/locations/{{location}}/zones/{{zone}}/networks/{{network_id}}'

network_id.description: A unique ID that identifies this network.

terraform_labels.description: The combination of labels configured directly on the resource and default labels configured on the provider.

update_time.description: The time when the subnet was last updated. A timestamp in RFC3339 UTC "Zulu" format, with nanosecond resolution and up to nine fractional digits. Examples: '2014-10-02T15:01:23Z' and '2014-10-02T15:01:23.045123456Z'.

zone.description: The name of the target Distributed Cloud Edge zone.
